Majic Product Version 5.1 has arrived, and I believe it represents the pinnacle of product photography workflows in the open-source ecosystem. I've combined two entirely different control approaches and put a lot of thought into how to automate and visualize the process. This version retains the product masking functionality, allowing you to use the masking editor to draw the areas you want to cover, and the workflow will automatically identify and calculate the relative size of these areas. Unfortunately, this workflow does not come with a corresponding LoRA model but instead uses IPAdapter to unleash the capabilities of the base model. Therefore, it's essential to choose a great base model that fits this workflow. Since IPAdapter is used, there’s no need to input prompts—simply let the corresponding pixels replace the text prompts. Lastly, I hope you can explore the potential of this workflow and learn something valuable from it. If you have the ability, you can even optimize this workflow further.


May you always maintain your passion and the courage to explore the unknown."


                               :SSsnap


Majic product Version5.1来了，我认为这是开源流程中顶尖的产品摄影工作流，我结合了两种截然不同的控制思路。我为他思考了很多，例如如何自动化，如何可视化。这一代版本并未舍弃产品遮挡的功能，你依然可以利用遮罩编辑器来绘制出你希望遮挡的区域，流程会自动化识别并计算这些区域的相对面积。遗憾的是这套流程并没有相应的lora模型，而是使用了ipadapter来激发出底模的能力。所以，你一定要选择一款很棒的底模来适配这套工作流程。因为使用了ip adapter所以我们无需填写提示词，只需要让相应的像素代替文本提示即可。最后，我希望你可以发掘出这套工作流的潜力，并从中学习到有用的知识，如果你有能力，还可以基于这套流程进行优化。



愿你永远保持激情和对未知事物探索的勇气


                   开源社区的无偿奉献着
                                :SSsnap

If we use two different versions of the model, sometimes the error "calculate_weight() got an unexpected keyword argument 'intermediate_dtype" will occur. I think it is probably because comfyui is not optimized enough, resulting in the wrong input of matrices of different versions and failure to multiply. There may be some problems with the calculate_weight() function. But I really don't know the specific reason, this is just my personal opinion.

如果我们使用了两个不同版本的模型。有时候会产生“calculate_weight() got an unexpected keyword argument 'intermediate_dtype”这个错误，我认为很可能是comfyui优化不足，导致不同版本的矩阵错误的传入，并无法相乘。calculate_weight() 函数可能有些问题。但我真的不知道具体原因，这只是我的个人见解。
